Name of project: Electronic Mouth Spray Oral Freshener,3 seconds fresh breath
Description: Electronic Mouth Spray Oral Freshener is an intelligent chip&MCU controller touch-sensing oral spray. It is easy to carry (small size and light weight), suitable for various occasions, and can freshen your breath in 3 seconds. It has a user-friendly design with 45°inclined nozzle and 360° full coverage of the mouth to increase the user’s experience. It has multiple flavors(white peach, grapefruit, lemon mint). Welcome to join us and give you a better experience.
